title: Shaker-style Cabinets, Walking Distance To Shopping, Pool
posting_body: Welcome To The Best of KentArterra’s apartments and townhomes are in a great location in the city of Kent, allowing residents to live a quiet life without being too far from the action.
Our two- and three-bedroom floor plans offer fireplaces, washer/dryers, walk-in closets, and private patios or decks.
Many have updated features such as stunning quartz countertops, faux wood flooring, and new cabinets.
As a resident, you can enjoy the clubhouse, brand-new playground, updated fitness center, business center, and a seasonal swimming pool.
Affordable living, a convenient location and great amenities make Arterra the perfect place to call home.
